item.title: 220 Madison Ave #6Q
item.dc:creator: cumulo
item.content:encoded: 220 Madison Ave #6Q Brand new to the market and priced to sell a 2 bedroom 2 Full bathroom home on Madison Avenue! This apartment features a gracious foyer large living room, a beautifully renovated kitchen with top of the line appliance and split bedroom layout. The master bedroom has city quiet windows as well as 2 exposures, and an en suite bath. The second bedroom also has an en suite bath. The apartment has abundant closet space and is located on a beautiful block on Madison Avenue. The building is beautifully maintained with new hallways, elevators and fantastic staff of full time doormen. This apart...ment will not last !!!

item.title: 64 E 80th St #2F
item.dc:creator: cumulo
item.content:encoded: 64 E 80th St #2F Dost Thou Love Me? (Romeo and Juliet, Act 2, Scene 2) Gracious Old World Townhouse ONE BEDROOM, Ideal Location!**Standing on the exquisite Juliet Balcony, overlooking one of the Upper East Side's most charming tree-lined blocks, you will SUCCUMB TO LOVE for this superb one bedroom apartment in a townhouse co-operative, built by renowned period architect Leopold Eidlitz in 1883. **Incomparably located on 80th St between Park and Madison, the building and the apartment retain all of their distinctive character, and many of the original pre-WWI details. (Once ensconced within, you may be t...ransported back in time and imagine a suitor calling up to your bedroom balcony.) Christopher Grey (NYT) describes the building as a brick and brownstone Victorian GEM with terraces, ironwork and knobby column capitals. **The living room features 10.2 foot ceilings, an enormous bay window, with interior wooden shutters, hardwood floors with woven woodwork trim and tall baseboards, a fireplace with hand painted tiles of SHAKESPEAREAN scenes, built-in bookcases, and tree top views over the street. **The bedroom possesses a wrought iron Juliet balcony outside the large French doors with arched transom light above, and a large walk-in closet. **The unique kitchen is designed with unfinished steel face cabinetry. There is a custom fabricated stainless sink with backsplash and a 9' deep bowl, dishwasher, water filter, and ample storage. The bathroom is in good condition, with white and black tiling. **This jewel apartment is on the third floor of a walkup building that has kept the original grace of these 19th Century classic ornamented brownstone homes. There is a washer/dryer and storage in the basement. Pied a terres are allowed. **It is located within steps of The Metropolitan Museum, Central Park, Museum Mile, and the Lenox Hill hospital. There are multiple bus lines and the 4, 5, 6 subway lines, nearby upscale, and neighborhood shopping options, art galleries, and noted restaurants. The WalkScore website ranks this location, a 99 for walkability (Walker's Paradise) and 100 for transit.**Apartment Features: high ceilings, bay window, fireplace, balcony, north exposure. **Building Features: ornamental stonework, wrought iron details, lovely woodwork in the halls and stairs, Laundry room.

item.title: 953 S Fetterly Ave
item.dc:creator: cumulo
item.content:encoded: 953 S Fetterly Ave Very well kept triplex located in a convenient as well as highly desired rental area of East Los Angeles. Perfect opportunity to live in one and rent the other two units! Don't miss this great investment opportunity!

item.title: 2170 Century Hl #805
item.dc:creator: cumulo
item.content:encoded: 5100 Cavanagh Rd NEW HOME FOR SALE. Custom built home in University Hills. This beautiful home has 4 bedrooms and 4 bathrooms. About 2,400 Sq. Ft. of living space. At the access floor, there is a two car garage and a laundry room attached to the garage. Three story building nestled into the hillside. Once you enter the front door, take the staircase onto the second floor and you'll walk in to a very beautiful and large open space. The kitchen has top of the line appliances, stone counter tops and custom built cabinets and a breakfast bar. There is also one bedroom with direct access to a bathroom on thi...s second floor. The third floor consist of average size master bedroom, a second bedroom with direct access to a beautiful hallway bathroom, and a third large master bedroom a large bathroom with a Jacuzzi bath tub. The flooring on hallways, living room and second floor bedroom is wood, kitchen and bathrooms have ceramic tiles, and carpet on third floor bedrooms. THIS IS A MUST SEE HOME.
